{"tid":1827811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賣港團體約見少數派議員　反對向香港電台增撥經費","createTime":"2020-01-17T08:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T11:26:10.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b22e3881eada25d202844bc7585d889027f18af5","tid":1827811,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:53:20.000Z","msg":"有團體在政總外請願，並約見建制派立法會議員，反對政府現階段向香港電台增撥經費。<br />\n<br />\n香港政研會約20人高舉標語，手持國旗。發言人表示，上星期四發起網上聯署，截至昨日收集約5萬人簽名，質疑香港電台每年用10億元公帑，以所謂新聞自由，發放不合邏輯及未經證實的資訊，亦有節目主持人訪問時態度差劣，影響市民對政府印象。<br />\n<br />\n發言人要求，辭退不稱職記者及工作人員，成立收視問責制度及內容監管制度，又建議開放31台時段，讓不同政見的市民製作民間節目。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會議員蔣麗芸說，每個城市總有傳媒機器，站在政府立場宣傳，特別關注「烽煙」及時事節目，不應有強烈立場。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1503339_1_20200117162414.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1503339_1_20200117162414.jpg&h=aa7f63a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503339-20200117.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503339-20200117.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyns01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=81324cea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503339-20200117.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f8276dfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503339-20200117.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"29ee07b9cc49c1ee6e7058f890b67da550d246c8","tid":1827811,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:54:01.000Z","msg":"成班垃圾"},{"pid":"0e6f193d9dbae461956af8ec98d55b9c5b04edd1","tid":1827811,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:58:39.000Z","msg":"少數派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acabca572603eb170d45c80b1a9e5119839d9a23"